<P>The &s;econd is the Ba&s;is of a Statue erected to the honour of one Cyrus, Son of Apollonius the mo&s;t excellent chief Phy&s;itian to the City, erected by the Corporation for his many benefactions to the City, Anointing them &s;plendidly and very &s;umptuou&s;ly and be&s;towing a Thou&s;and Atticks on the Corporation.</P>
